com.skobbler.ngx
Interface SKMapsDownloadListener

public interface SKMapsDownloadListener

Listener for download operations.
When downloads are done within the SKMaps library , the client that is registered with this listener can receive notifications about the status of the current downloads.

Version:
3.0

Method Summary
